OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start for much of
OL,6,FWales with some good sunny spells.
OL,7,FCloud will thicken as the day goes on,
OL,8,Fwith many places holding onto cloudy
OL,9,Fskies through the rest of the day.
OL,10,FFeeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLow cloud will spread across
OL,13,FWales during the evening and overnight
OL,14,Fwith a few spots of drizzle possible
OL,15,Fat times. Staying mild under the
OL,16,Fblanket of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
