OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA grey and murky start but
OL,6,Flargely dry. Outbreaks of rain will
OL,7,Fgradually move in from the south
OL,8,Fthrough the day, turning heavy over
OL,9,Fthe hills.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FFurther spells of rain are likely over
OL,13,Fthe next few days, but there will also
OL,14,Fbe some drier and brighter interludes
OL,15,Fat times. Feeling warm and
OL,16,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
